HEADWORD: Churrworm
<hw>Churr"worm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>cyrran</ets>, <ets>cerran</ets>, to turn.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
